Congratulations on hitting that landmark level!

Slyde

-----Original Message-----
From: Rosha Unca [mailto:captrosha@...]
Sent: Sunday, July 16, 2000 10:19 PM
To: eqbards@egroups.com
Subject: [eqbards] Toot my own horn


In my entire EQ career, I can honestly say I never said in shout, out
of character, or even guild chat, the word "ding". I rarely (to my
recollection) even said anything other than "Hold on a moment while I
scribe a new song". But, the time has come for me to shout "DING".
Rosha Cristi, born on March 26th, 1999 on the server of Innoruuk
finally achieved the 50th level after 65 days and 20 hours of
playtime. Many thanks go out to the people on this list from whom I
have learned many a thing about being a successful bard. Thank You.

Rosha Cristi, Bard of 50 {insert something musical here}
Guild Leader, Legends
Innoruuk
